summary: bbcstudiostalentworks: The class of 19. Slightly delayed post but this time last week there were lots of happy faces after a...
body: bbcstudiostalentworks: The class of 19. Slightly delayed post but this time last week there were lots of happy faces after a brilliant week at Bore Place. TalentWorks partnered with the BBC Writers Room to take eight bright stars in the digital talent space away on a scripted comedy writing retreat, learning everything from how to form a sitcom character, crafting a topical joke to just finding out the funny within you. We were totally blown away by the talent and can’t wait to see the ideas that flourish from the project. Thanks so much to everyone involved.
